    <item>
      <title>About</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/about/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/about/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Hi, I&amp;rsquo;m Kittisci. I am a British physics and maths teacher with an astrophysics degree. I love space, playing games, and building things!&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I have created this site as a way to collect my interests and tools into a single place while sharing these with any and all who happen across it.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;what-am-i-up-to-at-the-moment&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  What am I up to at the moment?&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#what-am-i-up-to-at-the-moment&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;active-projects&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  Active projects&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#active-projects&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Building this site&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;games&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  Games&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#games&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Sea of Thieves&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Umamusume Pretty Derby&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Overwatch&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;reading&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  Reading&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#reading&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;The Elsewhere Express by Samantha Sotto Yambao&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;site-info&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  Site info&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#site-info&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Kittisci went live on 2026-03-05 at kittisci-git.gihub.io using Hugo and the Coder theme&lt;br&gt;&#xA;Domain changed on 2026-03-07 to kittisci.co.uk&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
